City Hall will be lit Blue and White to support the&nbsp;2025 Oceania Track Championships.&nbsp;

The Oceania Cycling Championships is a collection of cycling competitions across several cycling disciplines held annually to determine the Oceania champion in each respective discipline. The Championships bring together the top track cyclists from Australia and New Zealand in a competition for individual and national honours.&nbsp;

This Light Up is organised by: Brisbane Economic Development Agency&nbsp;

